/***************************************************************************
 * Unified Threshold System
 * 
 * LOCATION-BASED THRESHOLDS:
 * - search_radius: Distance for nearby search results & traffic incidents (km)
 * - search_limit: Maximum number of results to return
 * 
 * EARTHQUAKE THRESHOLDS:
